## 2. Academic Schools & Programs
MRUH is a multidisciplinary university comprising several specialized schools offering industry-aligned innovative programs.

### School of Engineering
Focuses on emerging technologies and next-gen engineering disciplines.
*   **B.Tech Programs:**
    *   Computer Science & Engineering (CSE)
    *   CSE - Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning (AI & ML)
    *   CSE - Data Science
    *   CSE - Cyber Security
    *   CSE - Internet of Things (IoT)
    *   CSE - Blockchain Technology
    *   Cloud Computing

### School of Agriculture
Dedicated to advancing agricultural sciences and food technology.
*   **B.Sc. (Hons.) Programs:**
    *   Agriculture
    *   Horticulture
    *   Food Science & Technology

### School of Allied Healthcare Sciences
 preparing professionals for the modern healthcare sector.
*   **B.Sc. (Hons.) & Healthcare Programs:**
    *   Medical Laboratory Technology (MLT)
    *   Medical Imaging Technology (MIT)
    *   Anesthesia & Operation Theatre Technology
    *   Renal Dialysis Technology
    *   Optometry
    *   Cardiovascular Technology (CVT)
    *   Emergency Medicine Technology
    *   Forensic Science
    *   Biotechnology & Microbiology

### School of Management & Commerce
Nurturing future business leaders and entrepreneurs.
*   **Undergraduate:**
    *   BBA (Honors)
    *   B.Com (Honors)
*   **MBA (Master of Business Administration):**
    *   Specializations in: Human Resources (HR), Marketing, Finance, Business Analytics, Logistics & Supply Chain Management, and Healthcare & Hospital Management.

